@EndNode

@Node "_Backstdout"
_Backstdout-Pointer to the console window file handle

Synopsis

   BPTR _Backstdout;

Description

   _Backstdout is used by cback.o to point to the console window where I/O
   is to be routed.  If @{" _BackGroundIO " Link "_BackGroundIO"} is set to 1, cback.o initializes
   _Backstdout to point to the console window.  Otherwise, _Backstdout is
   not initialized.

   This variable is of interest only for background processes.  If you do
   not link with cback.o, this variable is ignored.

