   int error;                  /* 0 if successful */
   struct FileInfoBlock *info; /* file information area */

Portability

   AmigaDOS

Returns

   If the operation is successful, a value of 0 is returned.  Otherwise,
   the return value is -1, and you can find additional error information
   in @{" errno " Link "errno"} and @{" _OSERR " Link "_OSERR"}.

See Also

   @{" dfind() " Link "dfind()"} , @{" errno " Link "errno"} , @{" _OSERR " Link "_OSERR"}
