@Node "GfxBase"
GfxBase-Graphics Library Vector

Synopsis

   extern struct library * GfxBase;
   GfxBase = OpenLibrary("graphics.library",ver);

Description

   This external location is used by various Amiga library routines that
   interface with the ROM Kernel graphics system functions.  It must be
   initialized by an @{" OpenLibrary() " Link "exec/OpenLibrary()"} call before any of the graphics
   functions documented in the Amiga ROM Kernel manuals can be called.  It
   is expected to contain the base address of the graphics library vector
   table.  You must close the library before your program terminates.

Portability

   AmigaDOS
@EndNode

