@Node "__months"
__months-Array month lengths

Synopsis

   extern char __months[];

Description

   The external array __months contains twelve characters, each
   representing number of days in a specific month (in a non-leap year.)

   Your programs must account for leap years when dealing with February.

Portability

   @{" SAS/C " Link "Glossary - SASC"}

