@Node "vsprintf()"
vsprintf()-Varargs formatted write to string

Synopsis

   #include <stdio.h>
   #include <stdarg.h>

   x = vsprintf(buf, ctl, args);

   int x;            /* number of characters placed in the   */
                     /*   output buffer                      */
